content: Hi, i need stock of broken vowerk vaccuum.Broken, non functional no problem.https://bitify.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/20230303_093607**Important is that the engine inside has not been tampered with.You can make monthly residual just by going around your neigbourhood to tell them that you are interested in broken vowerk vaccuum.Note: i donot accept new one's! so donot go to break stores.I might need about 100 - 500 pieces per month if, possibleAlso, in order to save on cost of shipment to rome i'm setting a minimum of 10 piece before negotiation of payment.Only resident within the eu zone. At, a moment i cannot afford to pay for shipment & taxation for package outside the eu zone.RegardsBitcseo
